\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\sa360\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Although Scrivener is designed to be as stable as possible, and its auto-save should ensure your work is constantly saved, with important writing projects it\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s always a good idea to make regular backups, saved to either cloud services or external hard drives, so that your work is always safe no matter what happens.}
