\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\li763\fi-475\sa240\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::1> \tab 1.\tab Go to }{\f2\fs22\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>File > Back Up > Back Up Now<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 . This will create a new backup of the project in the automatic backups folder (as determined by the Options).}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0  \tab 2.\tab Go to }{\f2\fs22\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>File > Back Up > Back Up To\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8230\'85<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  You will be presented with a chooser dialog, allowing you to choose where the backup should be saved.<!$Scr_Ps::1>}}